## Technical Notes

1. **Framework Detection**: Identified Next.js 14.2.35 with App Router (app directory)
2. **Documentation Source**: Fetched latest instructions from https://vercel.com/docs/speed-insights/quickstart
3. **Package Manager**: Used npm (detected from existing package-lock.json)
4. **Integration Method**: Server Component compatible - SpeedInsights component works in both Server and Client Components

## Next Steps for Deployment

To enable Speed Insights data collection:
1. Deploy the application to Vercel
2. Navigate to Vercel Dashboard → Speed Insights
3. Select the project and click "Enable"
4. After deployment, the `/_vercel/speed-insights/*` routes will be available
5. Speed Insights data will appear in the dashboard after user visits

